{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"copy"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This string is displayed in the callout for the associated annotation."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"]]},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"subtitle","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"subtitle","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNAnnotation(py)subtitle","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"subtitle","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"abstract":[{"text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/subtitle":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle."}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle","title":"subtitle","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation"}}}